Webaverse is an open framework to build NFT-enabled virtual worlds using WebXR. Good places to start:

https://app.webaverse.com/

https://github.com/webaverse/docs
Webaverse is a framework that makes it easy for developers to build their own WebXR enabled virtual worlds and port NFTs into them

Webaverse is:

1) Accessible to all for free. No fees or downloads. Just a web URL to enter the open metaverse

2) 100% open source 

3) Fun and interaction - create GPT-3 enabled gameplay and narrative
